#!/usr/bin/env bash
# Print common media-util commands. Source the course media.env first.
#
# Usage: media-help

cat <<'EOF'
media-util — common commands
============================

Always start with (example: DJ4E):

  source /path/to/course/media.env
  cd /path/to/course

Build / refresh
---------------
  dump-youtube-playlist.sh              Dump YouTube playlist → youtube-playlist.jsonl
  compare-lessons-youtube.py            Diff lessons.json ↔ playlist JSONL
  compare-lessons-root.py               Diff lessons.json ↔ MEDIA_ROOT
  whisper-lessons                       Transcribe media listed in lessons.json
  whisper-media.sh                      Transcribe all media under MEDIA_ROOT
                                        (skips top-level archive/)
  whisper-cleanup.py                    Apply *whisper-replacements* to txt/vtt/srt
  whisper-desc                          AI title/tags/desc via Ollama (ollama serve)
  bootstrap-media-yaml.py               Build/refresh media.yaml
  update-lessons-from-media-yaml.py     Copy media.yaml titles + kaltura_id → lessons.json

After media.yaml is the source of truth — push to YouTube
----------------------------------------------------------
  test-youtube-oauth.py                 Smoke-test OAuth
  update-youtube-from-media-yaml.py                Dry-run
  update-youtube-from-media-yaml.py --apply        Apply all
  update-youtube-from-media-yaml.py --apply --only-playlist
  update-youtube-from-media-yaml.py --apply --limit 1
  update-youtube-from-media-yaml.py --apply --only VIDEO_ID
  update-youtube-from-media-yaml.py --apply --force-tags
                                        # retry tags when API list returns none

Kaltura (needs admin secret in media.env / ~/.ssh/kaltura_admin_secret)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
  test-kaltura.py                       Smoke-test partner + admin secret
  upload-kaltura-from-media-yaml.py              Dry-run missing kaltura_id
  upload-kaltura-from-media-yaml.py --apply --limit 1
  upload-kaltura-from-media-yaml.py --apply --only lesson-01-welcome
  upload-kaltura-from-media-yaml.py --apply --adopt
                                        # record existing referenceId match
  compare-kaltura-to-media-yaml.py      Scrape public playlist ↔ media.yaml (no API key)
  compare-kaltura.py                    Diff media.yaml ↔ Kaltura API (needs secret)
  kaltura-embed-urls                    Title + embed URL list from media.yaml
  kaltura-embed-urls -o embeds.txt

Check for drift
---------------
  dump-youtube-playlist.sh              Refresh playlist dump first
  compare-lessons.py                    Diff lessons.json ↔ media.yaml
  compare-media-root.py                 Diff MEDIA_ROOT ↔ media.yaml
  compare-youtube.py                    Diff media.yaml ↔ playlist
  compare-kaltura.py                    Diff media.yaml ↔ Kaltura
  compare-whisper-root.py               Orphan whisper artifacts
  compare-whisper-root.py --remove      Delete orphan whisper artifacts

One-off / local
---------------
  whisper-one.sh FILE                   Transcribe a single file (next to itself)
  whisper-folder.sh                     Transcribe top-level media in cwd

Docs: $MEDIA_UTIL/README.md  (or ../media-util/README.md next to the course)
EOF
